{"tid":570222,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"24歲少女湯新鈺失蹤兩日 你有冇見過？","createTime":"2018-02-23T12:16:31.000Z","updateTime":"2018-02-25T15:03:36.000Z","uid":122,"like":3,"dislike":76,"uniUserReply":60,"replies":[{"pid":"9e0fcf8b1466b5389c6e244331b60cd8ea6c27c5","tid":570222,"uid":122,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-23T12:16:31.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20180223/large/1519387563_1fe0.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20180223%2Flarge%2F1519387563_1fe0.jpg&h=741c441d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n24歲女子湯新鈺於前日(21日)下午在青衣牙鷹洲街最後露面後便告失蹤，其家人昨日(22日)向警方報案。<br />\n<br />\n湯新鈺身高約1.73米，體重約59公斤，中等身材，圓面型，黃皮膚，蓄染棕色及粉紅色長髮，右耳背、後頸、右手腕及左足踝有紋身。她最後露面時身穿黑色外套、深藍色牛仔褲及白色運動鞋。<br />\n<br />\n任何人如有湯新鈺的消息或曾見過她，請致電3661 1176或9689 7445，或電郵至rmpu-nts-2@police.gov.hk與新界南總區失蹤人口調查組，或與任何一間警署聯絡。"},{"pid":"ca105234f04264da3095c430cf2b4654b11eadae","tid":570222,"uid":6554,"like":239,"dislike":12,"score":227,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2018-02-23T12:20:59.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"8b977883d90e8aaa64710d3916f69951e72c424f","tid":570222,"uid":20619,"like":40,"dislike":2,"score":38,"quote":{"pid":"ca105234f04264da3095c430cf2b4654b11eadae","tid":570222,"uid":6554,"like":239,"dislike":12,"score":227,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2018-02-23T12:20:59.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-23T12:26:59.000Z","msg":"安全樣<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/agree2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ebca573f04bf15c4d9e792e022160affb0fc5159","tid":570222,"uid":19454,"like":6,"dislike":1,"score":5,"quote":{"pid":"ca105234f04264da3095c430cf2b4654b11eadae","tid":570222,"uid":6554,"like":239,"dislike":12,"score":227,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2018-02-23T12:20:59.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-23T13:28:07.000Z","msg":"X2"},{"pid":"7f2ad2e392adaf8aa3f64a576c0436ebd114cc66","tid":570222,"uid":49197,